{
  "stem": "3605.5",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "I should go there as soon as possible, and maybe I will still find him alive.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "Without any delay, there were the American occupation.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And Bergen-Belsen was in the English occupation.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "And there was a very fine American soldier that said, I'm a young girl, and I shouldn't travel alone.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "And there were two young Jewish men that wanted to go looking for their family too.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "And they assisted me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "And all the roads were still bombed, and there wasn't a good transportation.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "And he gave me a letter that the American soldiers, at every point, should send me as far as they can.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "And in three days, I managed to arrive to Bergen-Belsen.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "And I remember a point, that my girlfriend that I met in Minhen, was wearing a watch.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "When I saw her, she practically fainted and pointed to the watch.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "She had a little two-inch piece of paper-- that my brother said, I am in block 10.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "Come if you can.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "She told him that she is going to find me.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "And she showed him she had a watch that didn't ever work.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "And she put it in there instead of the work, and she gave me that.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "So I came there, and I knew exactly where-- where to look for my brother.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "And I came there, and I send in the two boys, because I was afraid that he's going to get a shock if he is going to-- if I walk in on him.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] Because the-- the-- the last time I-- I talked with him was in-- in Poland when I arrived to Piotrkow.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "I made a telephone to Tomaszow.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 60,
      "text": "And the next day, they rounded up all the people that were a day before on the telephone.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
